01:31:09,229 --> 01:31:12,063
is that physics works.

1595
01:31:12,064 --> 01:31:13,733
The Higgs, on the one hand,

1596
01:31:13,734 --> 01:31:16,035
completes the most successful
scientific theory

1597
01:31:16,036 --> 01:31:17,370
we've ever had,

1598
01:31:17,371 --> 01:31:19,205
on the other hand,
opens the door

1599
01:31:19,206 --> 01:31:24,577
to some very major paradoxes
that we now must address.

