01:31:27,480 --> 01:31:30,081
is steadfastly refusing
to push us

1602
01:31:30,082 --> 01:31:32,218
in one direction or the other:

1603
01:31:32,219 --> 01:31:33,986
the multiverse on the one side,

1604
01:31:33,987 --> 01:31:38,590
and some beautiful symmetry
on the other side.

1605
01:31:38,591 --> 01:31:42,402
It's cranking up the suspense
as much as it possibly can.

1606
01:31:48,167 --> 01:31:50,536
- Before the LHC started,
we would always say,

1607
01:31:50,537 --> 01:31:52,904
"New physics
is just around the corner."

1608
01:31:52,905 --> 01:31:54,239
And now we're kind of like,

1609
01:31:54,240 --> 01:31:55,942
"New physics
is still out there."

1610
01:31:55,943 --> 01:31:59,178
And, for one,
I'm not discouraged by this,

1611
01:31:59,179 --> 01:32:02,782
